• Loss & below step cap → Stake = Stake × 1.6 (controlled progression).
• Loss & step cap reached → reset Stake to base & restart cycle (escalation is capped).
• Win → reset Stake to base & clear loss streak (reset cycle).
• Total P&L, Stop-Loss or Max-Trades hit → pause trading for the session (circuit breaker).</comment>
